    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 91.</p><p>Heroic Perk: Hierophant’s Sanctuary</p><p>Prerequisite: Exalted Presence</p><p>You emit a permanent aura of protection in a 30-foot radius sphere centered on you. Friendly creatures within the area have a bonus to their saving throws equal to half your proficiency bonus (rounded down). When a friendly creature within the area is reduced to 0 hit points but not killed outright, you can use your reaction to have them be reduced to 1 hit point instead.</p></div>",
